SELECT /*+ set_var(new_planner_optimize_timeout = 2000) */ mocktable.business_line_name, mocktable.closetime, mocktable.complain_id, mocktable.complaintsource, mocktable.cpr_area_name, mocktable.dep_city, mocktable.dep_prov, mocktable.departure_date, mocktable.dest_province_name, mocktable.destination_city, mocktable.destination_country, mocktable.detail, mocktable.distribution_channel_id, mocktable.domain_name, mocktable.fault_category_name, mocktable.first_exam_target, mocktable.first_reason, mocktable.is_business_reason, mocktable.is_cpr_order, mocktable.is_examine, mocktable.issuetime, mocktable.local_tag, mocktable.order_date, mocktable.orderid, mocktable.pkg_region, mocktable.plc_prd_name, mocktable.pm_eid, mocktable.prd_line_name, mocktable.product_category_name, mocktable.product_id, mocktable.product_level_name, mocktable.product_pattern_name, mocktable.provider_id, mocktable.qa_pkgregion, mocktable.qa_region_name, mocktable.quality_id, mocktable.returndate, mocktable.sale_model_name, mocktable.second_exam_target, mocktable.second_reason, mocktable.source_from_name, mocktable.status, mocktable.themetagname, mocktable.tour_region_type, mocktable.vendor_name, mocktable.weekinput, SUM(mocktable.b_quality_cost) AS m_a0, SUM(mocktable.communication_cost) AS m_b1, SUM(CAST(mocktable.customerprice as DOUBLE)) AS m_c2, SUM(mocktable.paymentmoney) AS m_d3, SUM(mocktable.quality_cost) AS m_e4, SUM(mocktable.servicelabor_cost) AS m_f5
FROM (SELECT DISTINCT o.*, r.userno
FROM (SELECT a.*, b.sale_mode, b.dest_domain, b.dest_first_region, b.dest_second_region, b.bu_type, b.prd_pat_name, b.distr_channel, c.issuetime, c.closetime, c.complaintsource, d.detail, d.status, d.datachange_createtime, SUBSTR(d.datachange_createtime, 1, 10) AS datachange_createdate, b.dep_city, b.dep_prov, b.plc_prd_name, b.vendor_name, b.return_date AS returndate, b.cpr_area_name, b.plc_prd_tags, p.is_gold_guider_prd
FROM dw_diydb.adm_sev_qa_quality_dmt_t AS a
LEFT JOIN dw_diydb.edw_ord_tor_order_ext_d AS b ON (a.orderid = b.order_id)
LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT complaintsid, issuetime, closetime, complaintsource
FROM dw_diydb.vacationcomplaint_widetable
WHERE (d = '2023-07-26')) AS c ON (a.complain_id = c.complaintsid)
LEFT JOIN ods_vacdb.m_tourqualitycenterdb_qa_quality AS d ON (a.quality_id = d.quality_id)
LEFT JOIN (SELECT productid, is_gold_guider_prd
FROM dw_diydb.dim_prd_tor_pkg_ext
WHERE (d = '2023-07-26')) AS p ON (CAST(a.product_id as DOUBLE) = CAST(p.productid as DOUBLE))
WHERE ((b.d = '2023-07-26') AND (d.d = '2023-07-26'))) AS o
INNER JOIN (SELECT r1.*
FROM dw_diydb.vacation_permission AS r1
WHERE (LOWER(r1.userno) = LOWER('TR008959'))) AS r ON ((((((((COALESCE(o.sale_mode, '')) = (COALESCE(r.salemode, o.sale_mode, ''))) AND ((COALESCE(o.dest_domain, '')) = (COALESCE(r.domain, o.dest_domain, '')))) AND ((COALESCE(o.dest_first_region, '')) = (COALESCE(r.destfirstregion, o.dest_first_region, '')))) AND ((COALESCE(o.dest_second_region, '')) = (COALESCE(r.destsecregion, o.dest_second_region, '')))) AND ((COALESCE(o.bu_type, '')) = (COALESCE(r.butype, o.bu_type, '')))) AND ((COALESCE(o.prd_pat_name, '')) = (COALESCE(r.productpatternname, o.prd_pat_name, '')))) AND ((COALESCE(CAST(LOWER(o.distr_channel) as VARCHAR), '')) = (COALESCE(CAST(LOWER(r.distributionchannel) as VARCHAR), CAST(LOWER(o.distr_channel) as VARCHAR), ''))))) AS mocktable
WHERE (((((mocktable.qa_pkgregion = '广东代理组') AND ((mocktable.departure_date >= '2023-05-25') AND (mocktable.departure_date <= '2023-08-23'))) AND (mocktable.domain_name IN ('海外'))) AND ((mocktable.departure_date >= '2023-07-19') AND (mocktable.departure_date < '2023-07-26'))) AND (mocktable.is_examine = '是'))
GROUP BY mocktable.business_line_name, mocktable.closetime, mocktable.complain_id, mocktable.complaintsource, mocktable.cpr_area_name, mocktable.dep_city, mocktable.dep_prov, mocktable.departure_date, mocktable.dest_province_name, mocktable.destination_city, mocktable.destination_country, mocktable.detail, mocktable.distribution_channel_id, mocktable.domain_name, mocktable.fault_category_name, mocktable.first_exam_target, mocktable.first_reason, mocktable.is_business_reason, mocktable.is_cpr_order, mocktable.is_examine, mocktable.issuetime, mocktable.local_tag, mocktable.order_date, mocktable.orderid, mocktable.pkg_region, mocktable.plc_prd_name, mocktable.pm_eid, mocktable.prd_line_name, mocktable.product_category_name, mocktable.product_id, mocktable.product_level_name, mocktable.product_pattern_name, mocktable.provider_id, mocktable.qa_pkgregion, mocktable.qa_region_name, mocktable.quality_id, mocktable.returndate, mocktable.sale_model_name, mocktable.second_exam_target, mocktable.second_reason, mocktable.source_from_name, mocktable.status, mocktable.themetagname, mocktable.tour_region_type, mocktable.vendor_name, mocktable.weekinput
LIMIT 2000
